# Messaging Contracts and Buses

- Application job messages MUST implement `App\Shared\Application\Jobs\JobInterface`.
- Integration event messages MUST implement `App\Shared\Application\IntegrationEvents\IntegrationEventInterface`.
- Domain event messages MUST implement `App\Shared\Domain\Model\DomainEventInterface`.

## Bus semantics

- `domainEvent.bus` is for internal domain events only and SHOULD NOT route directly to AMQP transports.
- `integration.bus` is for integration events and SHOULD use the integration transport.
- `job.bus` is for asynchronous jobs and SHOULD use the job transport.

## Messenger routing convention

- Use interface-based Messenger routing, not per-class routing:
  - `IntegrationEventInterface` -> integration transport
  - `JobInterface` -> job transport
